  <Docs>
    <summary>
      The <c>URLSession</c> delegate object which enables network requests instrumentation. <i>It must be
      used together with</i> <c>DatadogRUM</c> or <c>DatadogTrace</c>.
      All requests made with the <c>URLSession</c> instrumented with this delegate will be intercepted by the SDK.
    </summary>
  </Docs>
